description: Experience a new kind of vacation at Sanata Villa. Surrounded by nature, our modern villas are built with comfort and convenience to ensure that your stay will be relaxing and enjoyable. From spacious bedrooms to private gardens, you’ll enjoy a peaceful getaway with your loved ones. Our villa has a fast internet connection, so you can stay connected with your friends and family. The swimming pool is also right outside the kitchen and living room area, so you can enjoy a relaxing break by the pool
